<h4 id="choose-your-route-styleclear-both">Choose Your Route {style=â€clear: both;â€}</h4>

<p><a href="http://pashley.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/burnout-paradise-20080701043017547_640w.jpg"><img src="/assets/img/burnout-paradise-20080701043017547_640w_thumb.jpg" alt="burnout-paradise-20080701043017547_640w" title="burnout-paradise-20080701043017547_640w" /></a></p>

